title: Gorgeous coed leaves college party for dorm, DISAPPEARS. Hear LATEST in search for Kristin Smart.
itunes:title: Gorgeous coed leaves college party for dorm, DISAPPEARS. Hear LATEST in search for Kristin Smart.
description:
After 24 years, new search warrants have been executed in the search for missing college student Kristin Smart. The 19-year-old California Polytechnic State University student was last seen walking back to her dorm room from an off-campus party. A spokesman for the San Luis Obispo County Sheriff’s Office says “some items of interest" have been recovered.

Joining Nancy Grace today:

  • Joe Scott Morgan- Forensics expert, Professor of Forensics Jacksonville State University, & author of"Blood Beneath My Feet"
  • Caryn Stark- NYC Psychologist
  • Shera LaPoint - Genetic Genealogist, "The Gene Hunter"
  • Anne Emerson- WCIV ABC 4 Charleston reporter
